# Alternates default widths while stepping around a loose spiral.

MOVE 60 60
SETHEADING 0
SETWIDTH 0.5

FORWARD 10
RIGHT 30
FORWARD 12
RIGHT 30
SETWIDTH 0.75
FORWARD 14
RIGHT 30
FORWARD 16
RIGHT 30
SETWIDTH 1.25
FORWARD 18
RIGHT 30
FORWARD 20
RIGHT 30
SETWIDTH 0.5
CIRCLE 10

MOVE 120 90
SETWIDTH 0.75
REPEAT 10
FORWARD 8
RIGHT 36
END